de></a></li></ol></li><li><a href=\"#\"><strong>Metody</strong></a><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineGetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__defineSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__defineSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupGetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupGetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupSetter__()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/hasOwnProperty\"><code>Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.prototype.isPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/propertyIsEnumerable\"><code>Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/setPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.setPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toLocaleString\"><code>Object.prototype.toLocaleString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>Metoda statyczna <strong><code>BigInt.asIntN</code></strong> jest używana do opakowywania wartości BigInt w wartości całkowite ze znakiem w zakresie od -2<sup>szerokość-1</sup> do 2<sup>szerokość-1</sup>-1.</p>\n\n<div id=\"sect2\"><iframe class=\"interactive\" height=\"692\" src=\"https://interactive-examples.mdn.mozilla.net/pages/js/bigint-asintn.html\" title=\"MDN Web Docs Interactive Example\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"składnia","title":"Składnia","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">BigInt.asIntN(<em>szerokość</em>, <var>bigint</var>);</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parametry","title":"Parametry","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"szerokość\"><code><var>szerokość</var></code></dt>\n <dd>Liczba bitów dostępnych dla rozmiaru wartości całkowitej (integer).</dd>\n <dt id=\"bigint\"><code><var>bigint</var></code></dt>\n <dd>Wartość całkowita, którą chcemy wpasować w daną liczbę bitów.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"wynik","title":"Wynik","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Wartość <code><var>bigint</var></code> modulo 2<sup><code><var>szerokość</var></code></sup> jako liczba całkowita ze znakiem.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"przykłady","title":"Przykłady","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"pozostawanie_w_zakresie_arytmetyki_64-bitowej","title":"Pozostawanie w zakresie arytmetyki 64-bitowej","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Metoda <code>BigInt.asIntN()</code> może być użyteczna do tego, by pozostać w zakresie obliczeń arytmetyki 64-bitowej.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> max <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token number\">2n</span> <span class=\"token operator\">**</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">64n</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> <span class=\"token number\">1n</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> <span class=\"token number\">1n</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nBigInt<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">asIntN</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">64</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> max<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// ↪ 9223372036854775807n</span>\n\nBigInt<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">asIntN</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">64</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> max <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token number\">1n</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// ↪ -9223372036854775807n</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// wartość ujemna ze względu na przepełnienie</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specyfikacje","title":"Specyfikacje","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specyfikacja</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://tc39.es/ecma262/#sec-bigint.asintn\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript (ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"pl\">The definition of 'BigInt.asIntN()' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Wsparcie przeglądarek","id":"wsparcie_przeglądarek","isH3":false,"query":"javascript.builtins.BigInt.asIntN","dataURL":"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/BigInt/asIntN/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"zobacz_też","title":"Zobacz też","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/BigInt\"><code>BigInt</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/BigInt/asUintN\"><code>BigInt.asUintN()</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Składnia","id":"składnia"},{"text":"Przykłady","id":"przykłady"},{"text":"Specyfikacje","id":"specyfikacje"},{"text":"Wsparcie przeglądarek","id":"wsparcie_przeglądarek"},{"text":"Zobacz też","id":"zobacz_też"}],"summary":"Metoda statyczna BigInt.asIntN jest używana do opakowywania wartości BigInt w wartości całkowite ze znakiem w zakresie od -2szerokość-1 do 2szerokość-1-1.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"BigInt.asIntN()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"BigInt.asIntN()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"BigInt.asIntN()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"BigInt.asIntN()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"BigInt.asIntN()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":